title: #92Noon! Montage/Talkers/Bercich/Kubiak/Parise
description: The Vikings season has ended. Montage, celebrating Justin Jefferson, Matt Birk all make up the first hour. Pete Bercich wraps the 2020 for the entire 10a hour, along with a cold call from Adam Thielen! Final stretch includes OC Gary Kubiak, and then Wild forward Zach Parise joins to end the show!
